#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:64
msgid ""
"為了方便使用這些資料，我們可以建立一個純文字文件 ``coord.txt``，再把兩地的座標資訊複製到文件中存檔，如此一來供 GMT "
"使用的資料表就建立完成。以下是使用十進位制座標的 ``coord.txt`` 內容："
msgstr ""
"We can create a text file ``coord.txt`` and save the coordinate information "
"to the file to easily access them later with GMT. Here's the content of "
"``coord.txt`` with the decimal formatted coordinates:"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:66
msgid ""
"47.92, 106.92\n"
"47.61, -122.33"
msgstr ""
"47.92, 106.92\n"
"47.61, -122.33"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:71
msgid ""
"再次強調，資料中的第一欄現在是緯度 (y 值)，第二欄是經度 (x 值)。這與我們在「\\ :doc:`scatter_plot`\\ "
"」一章中所使用的 xy 順序相反，不過只要適當的指定欄位意義，GMT 仍然可以讀取。另外，兩個欄位中間使用了「逗號」分隔，在 GMT "
"中也是可以接受的。"
msgstr ""
"Let me emphasize that the first column is latitude (y) and the second column "
"is longitude (x). This is opposite to the x-y order we used in the chapter "
":doc:`scatter_plot`. However, you'll see there is a way to specify the "
"meaning of each column so that GMT can still recognize them correctly. In "
"addition, we use commas to separate the columns here, which is acceptable "
"for GMT too."

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:73
msgid "以下是使用度分秒制座標的 ``coord.txt`` 內容："
msgstr "Here's the content of ``coord.txt`` with the d/m/s coordinates:"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:75
msgid ""
"47:55:0N, 106:55:0E\n"
"47:36:35N, 122:19:59W"
msgstr ""
"47:55:0N, 106:55:0E\n"
"47:36:35N, 122:19:59W"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:80
msgid ""
"注意我把所有的度分秒符號都統一成「冒號」，而且座標字串中間的空白都被移除了。這種格式是 GMT 接受的標準地理座標 (度分秒) "
"格式，如果你有一串地理座標資料是以度分秒格式儲存，記得在輸入 GMT 之前，把所有的度分秒符號都改為冒號，如上所示。"
msgstr ""
"Note that I have changed all the degree, minute, and second symbols to "
"colons and removed the space between the numbers. This is one of the "
"standard longitude and latitude formats for GMT. If your geographical "
"coordinates adopt this format, remember to check whether all the special "
"symbols have been converted into colons before feeding it to GMT, as this "
"example shows."

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:82
msgid ""
"你也可以從這裡下載資料檔：\\ :download:`coord.txt "
"<layout_design/coord.txt>`\\，這個版本使用度分秒制座標。"
msgstr ""
"You can also download the data from here: :download:`coord.txt <"
"layout_design/coord.txt>`. This file uses degrees, minutes, and seconds "
"coordinates."

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:86
msgid "簡單小結 GMT 對於文字輸入檔與地理座標格式的要求："
msgstr ""
"To summarize the requirements of data files and longitude and latitude "
"format for GMT:"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:88
msgid ""
"欄位的分隔符號可以是\\ **空白**\\ 、\\ **逗號** (``.csv`` 檔) 與 **Tab** (``.tsv`` 檔) "
"三者之一，但不能在同一個檔案中使用超過一種的分隔符號來分隔欄位。欄位代表的意義預設是第一欄 x 值、第二欄 y 值，不過可以在下指令時逐一指定。"
msgstr ""
"The acceptable delimiters for separating columns include **space**, **comma**"
" (as in ``.csv`` files), and **Tab** (as in ``.tsv`` files). However, you "
"cannot use more than one kind of delimiter in a single file. By default, the "
"first column is set to be the x value, and the second column is set to be "
"the y value. You can override this setting when reading them using a GMT "
"command."

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:89
msgid "地理座標可以採用\\ **十進位**\\ 或\\ **度分秒**："
msgstr ""
"The acceptable formats for geographical coordinates are **decimal** and **"
"degrees, minutes, and seconds**:"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:91
msgid "以十進位系統表示時，南緯要表示為負緯度，西經則表示為負經度或是東經 180 度之後持續累加，如經度 243 和 -63 都代表西經 63 度。"
msgstr ""
"For the decimal system, a negative latitude represents the southern "
"hemisphere, and a negative longitude or a longitude over 180 degrees "
"represents the western hemisphere. For example, both 243 and -63 are 63 "
"degrees W."

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:92
msgid ""
"以度分秒系統表示時，使用 ``ddd:mm:ssF`` 的方法，``ddd`` 為度，``mm`` 為分，``ss`` 為秒，``F`` 則是 "
"NEWS 四個字母之一。"
msgstr ""
"For the degrees, minutes, and seconds system, the format is ``ddd:mm:ssF`` "
"where ``ddd`` are degrees, ``mm`` are minutes, ``ss`` are seconds, and ``F`` "
"is a letter noting N, E, W, or S."

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:95
msgid "操作流程"
msgstr "Procedure"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:97
msgid "讓我們從目標地圖的下半部 (麥卡托投影的部份) 開始吧。先來畫出海岸線與國界："
msgstr ""
"Let's start from the lower part of the target map (the one using the "
"Mercator projection). First of all, we draw the coastlines and country "
"borders:"

#: ../../SOURCE_DOCS/layout_design.rst:99
msgid ""
"land_color=\"#CEB9A0\" # 陸域填色\n"
"\n"
"gmt begin ulaanbaatar_seattle png\n"
"    gmt basemap -R70/270/30S/70N -JM13c -B+tMercator\n"
"    gmt coast -Dl -A1000 -G$land_color -N1/thick,60 -Ba40f20g20\n"
"    # -D: 調整海岸線解析度。因為我們畫的是全球資料，用不著高解析度的海岸線，所以設定為 l (low) 即可。\n"
"gmt end"
msgstr ""
"land_color=\"#CEB9A0\" # Color for land area\n"
"\n"
"gmt begin ulaanbaatar_seattle png\n"
"    gmt basemap -R70/270/30S/70N -JM13c -B+tMercator\n"
"    gmt coast -Dl -A1000 -G$land_color -N1/thick,60 -Ba40f20g20\n"
"    # -D: Adjust the coastline resolution. We set it to l (low) because we "
"are drawing the global coastlines and do not need high-resolution data.\n"
"gmt end"

